      <title>银行家从佛罗里达州的增长热潮中收获了 150 亿美元的市政债券交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/bankers-reap-15-billion-of-muni-deals-from-florida-growth-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州向华尔街南部的转变正推动新移民的激增，对全州的基础设施造成冲击，并迫使各市政府以十多年来最快的速度借贷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/bankers-reap-15-billion-of-muni-deals-from-florida-growth-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:50:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>重组成为高风险借款人走向破产的捷径</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/restructuring-becomes-pit-stop-to-bankruptcy-for-risky-borrowers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的家电零件制造商 Robertshaw 去年达成了两项颇具争议的融资协议，试图维持运营。但今年，它还是申请了破产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/restructuring-becomes-pit-stop-to-bankruptcy-for-risky-borrowers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:31:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Resy 首席执行官认为消费者对餐饮的需求持续增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/resy-ceo-sees-consistent-consumer-demand-for-dining</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国运通旗下预订平台 Resy 的首席执行官 Pablo Rivero 在彭博电视上表示，他仍然看到消费者对餐厅用餐的强劲需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-07/resy-ceo-sees-consistent-consumer-demand-for-dining</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:31:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受乌克兰管道问题影响，欧洲天然气价格上涨至 2024 年高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/european-gas-rises-to-2024-high-on-ukraine-pipeline-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，乌克兰军队占领了天然气运输要地苏贾后，欧洲天然气价格飙升至今年最高水平。]]></description>
