    <item>
      <title>加拿大航空称巴黎奥运会影响今年夏季的销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/air-canada-profit-drops-weighed-down-by-pressure-on-airfares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大航空公布季度利润下降 47%，原因是主要市场（包括法国）的需求疲软，而今年夏天由于奥运会的缘故，一些旅客选择避开法国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/air-canada-profit-drops-weighed-down-by-pressure-on-airfares</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 11:10:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
